  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• An overview of a new generation high field spherical tokamak, ST40, is presented. • The mechanical structure, magnets and power supplies are described. • The main objectives of the ST40 experimental program are outlined. • Some of the challenges of constructing compact high field devices are discussed.</subfield>
